---
title: Carb Smart California-Inspired Chicken Salad with Avocado-Ranch Dressing and Seed Blend
description: Tonight's fresh, California-inspired salad is layered with peppery radishes, crips cucumber, crunchy seeds and the ultimate zippy guacamole-ranch dressing!

